    <div class="main-content">
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Digital Products</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">As a provider of online digital marketing courses, we do not offer physical products that require shipping or delivery. All our course materials and content are delivered electronically through our website and online learning platform.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Access To Digital Courses</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">1.1 <strong>Enrollment Confirmation:</strong> Upon successful enrollment in our digital marketing courses, you will receive a confirmation email containing details about your course, including access instructions and login credentials, if applicable. <br> 1.2 <strong>Instant Access:</strong> In most cases, you will have instant access to the course materials and content after completing the enrollment process and payment. <br> 1.3 <strong>Login Information:</strong> If a username and password are required for course access, please keep this information confidential and do not share it with others.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Support And Assistance</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">2.1 <strong>Technical Support:</strong> If you encounter technical issues or have questions regarding course access, please contact our customer support team at [Insert Contact Information]. We are here to assist you and ensure a smooth learning experience.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Refund And Cancellation</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">3.1 <strong>Refund Policy:</strong> Our refund policy for digital courses is outlined in our <a href="https://koshank.com/cancellation-and-refund/">Cancellation and Refund Policy</a>. Please review this policy for information on cancellation and refund options.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Additional Information</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">4.1 <strong>Course Materials:</strong> Upon successful enrollment in our digital marketing courses, you will receive a confirmation email containing details about your course, including access instructions and login credentials, if applicable. <br> 4.2 <strong>Course Access Period:</strong> The duration of your course access will be specified in the course description and enrollment confirmation. Please make the most of this access period to complete the course and access all relevant content. <br> 4.3 <strong>Updates And Revisions:</strong> We may periodically update and revise course content to ensure its relevance and accuracy. You will have access to the latest course materials during your enrollment period.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Changes To Policy</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">5.1 We reserve the right to update or modify this Shipping and Delivery Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be reflected on this page.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: left;">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="main-content__body" data-lead-id="main-content-body" style="text-align: left;">If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Shipping And Delivery Policy, please contact us at:<br><br>Koshank<br>Email: koshank.com@gmail.com <br><br>Thank you for trusting us with your personal information. We are committed to maintaining your privacy and providing you with quality digital marketing courses.</p>
